history.proof: intros a b c l H. destruct H as [H1 | H2]. - injection H1 as H3 H4 H5. left. split; [apply H3 | split; [apply H4 | apply H5]]. - right. apply H2.

original: intros a b c l H. simpl in H. destruct H as [H1 | H2]. - injection H1 as H3 H4 H5. left. split; [apply H3 | split; [apply H4 | apply H5]]. - right. apply H2.
